Floyd Mayweather continues his preparation and training for the Fight of the Century against Manny Pacquiao as the pair prepare for a $300m face-off on May 2 in Las Vegas.

The unbeaten 38-year-old has once again shared some images from inside his training camp, this time including some skipping and pad work with his father Floyd Mayweather Sr.

Mayweather has previously shared pictures and videos with the boxing universe, including one workout with Phil Collins playing in the background.  

